  <entry>
    <title>爬楼梯</title>
    <url>/2023/10/16/%E7%88%AC%E6%A5%BC%E6%A2%AF/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="爬楼梯"><a href="#爬楼梯" class="headerlink" title="爬楼梯"></a>爬楼梯</h1><p><a class="link"   href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/climbing-stairs/solutions/286022/pa-lou-ti-by-leetcode-solution/" >70. 爬楼梯 - 力扣（LeetCode） <i class="fa-regular fa-arrow-up-right-from-square fa-sm"></i></a></p>
<p>题目</p>
<p><img  
                     lazyload
                     src="/images/loading.svg"
                     data-src="https://qwe-pic.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/images/202310162027838.png"
                      alt=" "
                ></p>
<h2 id="分析"><a href="#分析" class="headerlink" title="分析"></a>分析</h2><p>共x阶台阶</p>
<p>$$f(x)$$只能由$$f(x-1)$$和$$f(x-2)$$通过加一或者加二过来。</p>
<p>$$<br>f(x)&#x3D;f(x−1)+f(x−2)<br>$$</p>
<h3 id="法一：动态规划"><a href="#法一：动态规划" class="headerlink" title="法一：动态规划"></a>法一：动态规划</h3><div class="highlight-container" data-rel="C"><figure class="iseeu highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">climbStairs</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> n)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> p = <span class="number">0</span>, q = <span class="number">0</span>, r = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; ++i) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        p = q;</span><br><span class="line">        q = r;</span><br><span class="line">        r = p + q;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> r;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<p>​	通过p，q的动态存储$$f(x-1)$$和$$f(x-2)$$来节约空间</p>
<h3 id="法二：记忆化递归"><a href="#法二：记忆化递归" class="headerlink" title="法二：记忆化递归"></a>法二：记忆化递归</h3><div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Plaintext"><figure class="iseeu highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>



<h3 id="法三：通项公式"><a href="#法三：通项公式" class="headerlink" title="法三：通项公式"></a>法三：通项公式</h3><div class="highlight-container" data-rel="C"><figure class="iseeu highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">climbStairs</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> n)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">double</span> sqrt5 = <span class="built_in">sqrt</span>(<span class="number">5</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">double</span> fibn = <span class="built_in">pow</span>((<span class="number">1</span> + sqrt5) / <span class="number">2</span>, n + <span class="number">1</span>) - <span class="built_in">pow</span>((<span class="number">1</span> - sqrt5) / <span class="number">2</span>, n + <span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> (<span class="type">int</span>) round(fibn / sqrt5);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

]]></content>
